                </div>
                
                <div class="security-item">
                    <div class="security-icon">‚Ä¢</div>
                    <div class="security-text">If you continue to have issues, please contact our support team</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="color: #157A6E; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                We're here to help you get back to learning! üìö‚ú®
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="company-info">
                <div class="company-name">Quiz-Blog Rwanda</div>
                <div class="company-tagline">Quizzing & Blogging</div>
                <div class="company-location">üìç Kigali | Rwamagana, Rwanda</div>
            </div>

            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/quiz-blog/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">LinkedIn</a>
                <span class="separator">|</span>
