                <a href="https://www.quizblog.rw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">Website</a>
                <span class="separator">|</span>
                <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=250780579067" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">üì± WhatsApp</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>